sentences: Edward E. Cherry Jr. (October 12, 1954) is an American jazz guitarist and studio musician.
Cherry is perhaps best known for his long association with trumpeter Dizzy Gillespie, with whom he performed from 1978 until shortly before Gillespie's death in 1993.
